# =============================================================================
# TARJETA CRC - .dockerignore (Exclusion de build context)
# =============================================================================
# Responsabilidades:
# - Evitar que secretos, caches y artefactos entren al build context.
# - Reducir tamano del contexto para builds mas rapidos.
#
# Colaboradores:
# - Dockerfiles (apps/backend, apps/frontend)
# - .gitignore (reglas espejo)
# - scripts/security/verify_no_secrets.sh
#
# Invariantes:
# - NO incluir .env reales ni secretos en el build context.
# - Mantener alineado con .gitignore en patrones criticos.
# =============================================================================

# Root-level dockerignore for repo hygiene

# VCS
.git

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Node / build outputs
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/
dist/
build/
.next/
.turbo/

# Python caches
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Coverage
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage/
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.nyc_output/

# Test artifacts
playwright-report/
test-results/

# Env / logs / temp
.env
.env.*
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak

# Secret folders / files
**/secrets/
*.secret
*.pem
*.key

# Cookies
cookies.txt
cookies*.txt
